text:
Make sure you read the Ts&Cs about Exchange Games…. I spent a bit of time investigating this recently to find that most of the money in the markets actually belongs to Betfair, And the money is placed there as a priority over the users money, so any First-To-Market strategies simply wont work.

Wasted a couple of nights coding before I learned this, would hate to see someone else do the same.
